# The Wizard's Tower

A simple 2D platformer for PC with a challenging mouse input twist.

## Concept

Navigate through a mystical tower using unconventional mouse-based controls. The wizard's tower is full of magical challenges and platforming puzzles.

## Features

- Pixel art graphics with retro charm
- Innovative control scheme using mouse movements
- Challenging platforming mechanics
- Progressive difficulty through tower levels

## Gameplay Mechanics

- Mouse-driven character movement
- Physics-based jumping and climbing
- Collectible magical artifacts
- Hidden secrets in each level

## Art Style

Beautiful pixel art inspired by classic platformers with a magical twist. Each floor of the tower has its own unique theme and color palette.

## Development Status

Currently in beta testing. Expected release Q2 2025.
